These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: spinach, apple, carrot
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, paramedic, journalist
1. the person eating spinach is in an even position##4
2. the electrician is on the left or right of the journalist##3
3. the electrician is the person eating apple##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the far left##1
5. the paramedic is the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | spinach | apple |
| Job    | paramedic    | journalist | electrician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, writing, camping
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, airplane, quad-bike
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person driving the airplane is the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | writing | camping | magic-tricks |
| Transport   | quad-bike    | airplane     | car        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, camping, collecting
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, classical, punk
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | collecting     | camping | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | classical | metal     | punk  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, crime, satire
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, swimming, handball
1. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | crime  | disaster  |
| Sport         | weightlifting  | swimming | handball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, rock-climbing, filmmaking
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, egyptian, australian
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is writing and the indian##2
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
3. the australian is on the left of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | writing   | filmmaking | rock-climbing    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | australian     | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, sudoku, drawing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming, cycling
1. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | sudoku | drawing | writing   |
| Sport   | cycling     | ice-hockey    | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, romance, action
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rabbit, bird
1. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is between the owner of the bird and the person watching action movies##2
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | spy | romance |
| Pet           | rabbit         | hedgehog         | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, cherry, grapes
3 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, turtle
1. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the lizard and the person eating cranberry##2
2. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | cherry | grapes | cranberry |
| Pet    | lizard    | ferret | turtle     |

