.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, house
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, skiing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | house   | hip-hop  | gospel  |
| Sport         | skateboarding | skiing | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, cauliflower, cucumber
1. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person eating cucumber is in an even position##4
3. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk      | tea |
| Food       | cauliflower | cucumber | watermelon   |

