.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, social-worker, paramedic
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, quad-bike, van
1. the paramedic is on the right of the social-worker##1
2. the person driving the tram is the chef##1
3. the person driving the van is the paramedic##1
4. the paramedic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | social-worker | paramedic | chef |
| Transport   | quad-bike | van   | tram |

