2. the spanish is the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the japanese##3
4. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | turkish | japanese | spanish |
