.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, magic-tricks, video-games
3 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, frog
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | video-games | hiking |
| Pet     | mouse    | frog  | guinea-pig   |

