There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, mexican, japanese
1. the japanese is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | tea | milk | mirinda |
| Nationality   | mexican   | japanese          | nigerian |

