.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, frog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, cycling, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | mouse  | frog   | chinchilla |
| Sport   | badminton | cycling | skateboarding       |

 